0.0.1.name: wordpress/quicktags
0.0.1.description: Allows for front-end tagging of posts. It uses jQuery UI autocomplete to search the WP DB and return the closest matching tag based on the search term. If no tag was found, you can add a new tag by simply hitting the enter key.
